{"id":118726,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/简讯：缅甸当局敦促民众投票/","date":"2010-11-01T20:38:30Z","modified":"2010-11-01T20:38:30Z","title":"简讯：缅甸当局敦促民众投票","content":"<div>\n<p>缅甸军人政府敦促民众踊跃参加下月的大选。这是20多年来缅甸首次举行大选。</p>\n<p>国营媒体说，如果人们抵制投票或投票人数不足，现任政府将继续掌控权利。</p>\n<p>20年前，缅甸军政府拒绝向大选中获胜的昂山素季领导的全国民主联盟交出权力。</p>\n<p>联合国对即将举行的选举的合法性提出质疑，并表示两千多政治异见人士仍在狱中。</p>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QJRCMEfsPhrSERAG_dXwATj9I_8/0/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QJRCMEfsPhrSERAG_dXwATj9I_8/0/di\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QJRCMEfsPhrSERAG_dXwATj9I_8/1/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QJRCMEfsPhrSERAG_dXwATj9I_8/1/di\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/fg30Qwz3Xz0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></p>\n","author":1,"categories":[8779],"tags":[11961]}